%2Fndtvindia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40ndtvindia%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FbYLT5BuvQh%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FbYLT5BuvQh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Uma%20Sudhir%20(%40umasudhir)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fumasudhir%2Fstatus%2F1742354352105460058%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%203%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20the%20delivery%20agent%20could%20be%20heard%20talking%20to%20a%20passerby%20that%20he%20opted%20to%20arrive%20on%20horseback%20to%20deliver%20the%20food%20after%20the%20pumps%20ran%20out%20of%20petrol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20what%20had%20happened%2C%20the%20horse-rider%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BPetrol%20nahi%20mila%20bhai.%20Teen%20ghante%20line%20me%20khada%20raha.%20Zomato%20se%20nikal%20gaya..petrol%20nahi%20mila.(There%20was%20no%20petrol.%20I%20waited%20in%20the%20queue%20for%20three%20hours.%20I%20left%20after%20taking%20the%20order%20but%20couldn't%20get%20the%20petrol).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELong%20queues%20spilled%20over%20to%20the%20main%20roads%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20Tuesday%20as%20a%20large%20number%20of%20motorists%20gathered%20at%20the%20fuel%20outlets%20for%20petrol%20and%20diesel%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20resulting%20in%20traffic%20jams%20at%20several%20places%20for%20some%20time%2C%20news%20agency%20PTI%20reported.%20The%20traffic%20jam%20was%20brought%20under%20control%20by%20evening%2C%20police%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(Fuel)%20availability%20is%20there.%20People%20are%20apprehensive%20that%20due%20to%20the%20agitation%20by%20truck%20drivers%2C%20it%20may%20not%20be%20available%20and%20they%20are%20going%20to%20petrol%20pumps%20in%20large%20numbers%2C%20following%20which%20queues%20were%20formed%20and%20subsequently%20spilled%20over%20to%20the%20roads%20resulting%20in%20traffic%20jams%20initially%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20police%20official%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20petrol%20reta