uffered%20the%20same%20emotional%20and%20psychological%20trauma%20as%20someone%20who%20has%20been%20raped%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Breal%20world%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20first%20virtual%20sexual%20offence%20investigated%20by%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20child%20experienced%20psychological%20trauma%20similar%20to%20that%20of%20someone%20who%20has%20been%20physically%20raped.%20There%20is%20an%20emotional%20and%20psychological%20impact%20on%20the%20victim%20that%20is%20longer%20term%20than%20any%20physical%20injuries%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20officer%20familiar%20with%20the%20case%20told%20the%20news%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20poses%20a%20number%20of%20challenges%20for%20law%20enforcement%20given%20current%20legislation%20is%20not%20set%20up%20for%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20remains%20unclear%20what%20game%20the%20teenage%20girl%20was%20playing%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20alleged%20offence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20into%20the%20landmark%20case%20has%20now%20prompted%20questions%20about%20whether%20police%20should%20be%20pursuing%20virtual%20offences%2C%20given%20police%20and%20prosecutors%20are%20currently%20struggling%20with%20an%20enormous%20backlog%20of%20actual%20rape%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20UK%20Home%20Secretary%20James%20Cleverly%20has%20defended%20the%20virtual%20reality%20rape%20probe%20saying%20that%20the%20child%20has%20gone%20through%20%26quot%3Bsexual%20trauma%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20it%20is%20easy%20to%20dismiss%20this%20as%20being%20not%20real%2C%20but%20the%20whole%20point%20of%20these%20virtual%20environments%20is%20they%20are%20incredibly%20immersive%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Cleverly%20told%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fpolice-investigate-rape-metaverse%2F%5C%22%3Enews%20outlet%20LBC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20also%20worth%20realising%20that%20somebody%20who%20is%20willing%20to%20put%20a%20child%20through%20a%20trauma%20like%20that%20digitally%20may%20well%20be%20someone%20that%20could%20go%20on%20to%20do%20terrible%20things%20in%20the%20physical%20realm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Has%20Meta%20Responded%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20several%20reports%20of%20virtual%20sex%20crimes%20in%20Horizon%20Worlds%20%E2%80%94%20a%20free%20VR%20game%20operated%20by%20Facebook's%20parent%20company%2C%20Meta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20kind%20of%20behaviour%20described%20has%20no%20place%20on%20our%20platform%2C%20which%20is%20why%20for%20all%20users%20we%20have%20an%20automatic%20protection%20called%20personal%20boundary%2C%20which%20keeps%20people%20you%20don't%20know%20a%20few%20feet%20away%20from%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Meta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704252780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-08%2Fuk-police-buckingham-palace-knife-attack-reuters_650x400_51503702916.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-girl-virtually-gang-raped-metaverse-virtual-reality-game-cops-begin-probe-meta-4790442%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Police%20in%20the%20UK%20are%20investigating%20the%20first%20case%20of%20an%20alleged%20rape%20in%20a%20virtual%20reality%20game%20after%20a%2016-year-old%20girl%20was%20%26quot%3Bsexually%20attacked%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20online%20%26quot%3Bmetaverse%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-girl-virtually-gang-raped-metaverse-virtual-reality-game-cops-begin-probe-meta-4790442%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-girl-virtually-gang-raped-metaverse-virtual-reality-game-cops-begin-probe-meta-4790442%2Fa