20being%20made%20by%20the%20local%20authorities%2C%20police%2C%20firefighters%20and%20other%20operational%20units%2C%20while%20the%20number%20of%20personnel%20and%20rescue%20dogs%20is%20enhanced.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20we%20ask%20you%20to%20remain%20fully%20mindful%20that%20we%20are%20in%20a%20race%20against%20time%20and%20to%20continue%20to%20do%20your%20utmost%20to%20save%20lives%2C%20putting%20people's%20lives%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20Kishida%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20operation%20was%20given%20extra%20urgency%20as%20the%20Japan%20Meteorological%20Agency%20(JMA)%20issued%20a%20heavy%20rain%20warning%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBe%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20landslides%20until%20the%20evening%20of%20Wednesday%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20coastal%20city%20of%20Suzu%2C%20mayor%20Masuhiro%20Izumiya%20said%20there%20were%20%26quot%3Balmost%20no%20houses%20standing%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAbout%2090%20percent%20of%20the%20houses%20(in%20the%20town)%20are%20completely%20or%20almost%20completely%20destroyed...%20the%20situation%20is%20really%20catastrophic%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20broadcaster%20TBS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20at%20a%20shelter%20in%20the%20town%20of%20Shika%20told%20TV%20Asahi%20that%20she%20%26quot%3Bhasn't%20been%20able%20to%20sleep%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20aftershocks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20scared%20because%20we%20don't%20know%20when%20the%20next%20quake%20will%20hit%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%2034%2C000%20households%20were%20still%20without%20power%20in%20Ishikawa%20prefecture%2C%20the%20local%20utility%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20cities%20were%20without%20running%20water.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShinkansen%20bullet%20trains%20and%20highways%20have%20resumed%20operations%20after%20several%20thousand%20people%20were%20stranded%2C%20some%20for%20almost%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Geological%20Survey%20said%20the%20quake%20had%20a%20magnitude%20of%207.5%2C%20while%20the%20JMA%20measured%20it%20at%207.6%2C%20triggering%20a%20major%20tsunami%20warning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20powerful%20quake%20was%20one%20of%20more%20than%20400%20to%20shake%20the%20region%20through%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20the%20JMA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapan%20lifted%20all%20tsunami%20warnings%20after%20waves%20at%20least%201.2%20metres%20(four%20feet)%20high%20hit%20the%20town%20of%20Wajima%20and%20a%20series%20of%20smaller%20tsunamis%20were%20reported%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapan%20experiences%20hundreds%20of%20earthquakes%20every%20year%20and%20the%20vast%20majority%20cause%20no%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20earthquakes%20in%20the%20Noto%20Peninsula%20region%20has%20been%20steadily%20increasing%20since%202018%2C%20a%20Japanese%20government%20report%20said%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20is%20haunted%20by%20a%20massive%209.0-magnitude%20undersea%20quake%20off%20northeastern%20Japan%20in%202011%2C%20which%20triggered%20a%20tsunami%20that%20left%20around%2018%2C500%20people%20dead%20or%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20swamped%20the%20Fukushima%20atomic%20plant%2C%20causing%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20worst%20nuclear%20disasters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704248280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Ff2afmmr_japan-earthquake_625x300_02_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjapan-earthquake-death-count-rises-to-57-officials-warn-of-more-quakes-4790023%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20death%20count%20in%20Japan%20has%20now%20risen%20to%2057%20following%20a%207.5-magnitude%20earthqua