%20her%20innocence%2C%20Banerjee%20demanded%20a%20processing%20fee%20of%20Rs%2096%2C525.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20scam%20unfolded%2C%20the%20fraudulent%20officer%20escalated%20the%20situation%20by%20alleging%20the%20involvement%20of%20bank%20officials%20in%20the%20money%20laundering%20scheme.%20To%20close%20the%20case%20and%20avoid%20potential%20legal%20consequences%2C%20Ms%20Patil%20was%20coerced%20into%20transferring%20an%20additional%20Rs%204%2C83%2C291%20to%20a%20Punjab%20National%20Bank%20account%20controlled%20by%20the%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20later%2C%20Ms%20Patil%20confided%20in%20her%20landlord%20about%20the%20incident%2C%20only%20to%20realise%20that%20she%20had%20fallen%20victim%20to%20a%20well-orchestrated%20cyber%20scam.%20The%20actor%20reported%20the%20incident%20to%20the%20DN%20Nagar%20Police%2C%20who%20promptly%20registered%20a%20case%20and%20initiated%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704246600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fbm23m8n_anjali-patil-actor-instagram_625x300_03_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbollywood-actor-duped-of-rs-5-79-lakh-by-scammer-posing-as-mumbai-cop-report-4790346%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bollywood%20actor%20Anjali%20Patil%20was%20duped%20of%20Rs%205.79%20lakh%20by%20a%20cyber%20fraud%20posing%20as%20a%20Mumbai%20Police%20officer%2C%20a%20report%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbollywood-actor-duped-of-rs-5-79-lakh-by-scammer-posing-as-mumbai-cop-report-4790346%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbollywood-actor-duped-of-rs-5-79-lakh-by-scammer-posing-as-mumbai-cop-report-4790346%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbollywood-actor-duped-of-rs-5-79-lakh-by-scammer-posing-as-mumbai-cop-report-4790346%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prior%20%26amp%3B%20post%20facto%20green%20nods%20can't%20co-exist%2C%20SC%20told%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704246148000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106498325%2Cimgsize-532656.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fprior-post-facto-green-nods-cant-co-exist-supreme-court-told%2Farticleshow%2F106498038.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22DHANANJAY%20MAHAPATRA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Looking%20Beyond%20Politics%2C%20Constitution%20and%20Law%3A%20How%20the%20People%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Feel%20About%20SC%E2%80%99s%20Decision%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F11100850%2FUntitled-design-14-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20confirmed%20the%20proclamation%20made%20on%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20August%205%2C%202019%20to%20read%20down%20Article%20370.%20This%20has%20been%20welcomed%20by%20a%20majority%20of%20those%20in%20the%20mainland.%20But%20who%20cares%20about%20the%20people%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3F%20Though%20its%20constitutional%20validity%20is%20still%20being%20debated%20by%20some%20well-known%20legal%20luminaries%2C%20including%20former%20judges%2C%20the%20highest%20court%20of%20the%20country%20has%20given%20its%20final%20verdict%20and%20it%20is%20unlikely%20to%20face%20any%20challenge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESetting%20aside%20politics%2C%20constitution%20and%20law%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20human%20aspect%20to%20consider%3A%20How%20do%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%201.6%20crore%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20feel%20about%20the%20decision%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20move%20uphold%20it%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EUnfortunately%2C%20the%20media%20is%20silent%20on%20this%20aspect.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20spoke%20to%20many%20people%20and%20their%20families%20across%20districts.%20As%20their%20doctor%20for%20several%20decades%20and%20having%20earned%20their%20trust%2C%20they%20spoke%20their%20heart%20out.%20Their%20feelings%20and%20emotions%20are%20summed%20up%20in%20this%20article.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20Maharaja%20Hari%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20rule%20came%20to%20an%20end%20with%20conditional%20accession%20to%20India%20in%20October%201947%2C%20Kashmiris%20in%20general%20have%20been%20a%20calm%20and%20content%20people.%20Everybody%20has%20a%20house%20to%20live%20in%2C%20adequate%20clothes%20to%20wear%20and%20enough%20to%20eat%2C%20and%20villagers%20have%20a%20piece%20of%20agricultural%20land%20too%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20revolutionary%20land%20reforms%20by%20its%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Mohammed%20Abdullah.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20were%20happy%20that%20they%20were%20not%20made%20to%20join%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20had%20a%20reasonably%20comfortable%20relationship%20with%20India%20with%20their%20identity%20intact.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20people%20of%20the%20Kashmir%20valley%2C%20the%20most%20well-known%20part%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20are%20an%20Indo-Aryan%20ethnolinguistic%20group%20who%20speak%20the%20Kashmiri%20language.%20The%20language%20has%20its%20origin%20in%20Dardic%20with%20words%20from%20Sanskrit%2C%20Persian%20and%20Punjabi%20mixed%20together.%20The%20predominant%20religion%20of%20the%20valley%20today%20is%20Islam%20but%20it%20was%20not%20so%20always.%20It%20used%20to%20be%20Buddhism%2C%20taken%20over%20by%20Shaivism%20in%209%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century.%20Islam%20took%20roots%20during%2013%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%2015%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%20and%20today%20Kashmir%20is%20predominantly%20Muslim.%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%2C%20a%20minority%20with%20around%20120%2C000%20population%2C%20were%20living%20in%20great%20harmony%20with%20the%20Muslims%20in%20the%20valley%20till%20the%20unfortunate%20exodus%20of%20some%20100%2C000%20persons%20in%201990.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20religions%20like%20Sikhism%20and%20Christianity%20constitute%20at%20the%20most%201.5%25%20of%20the%20population.%20The%20people%20had%20their%20chosen%20representatives%2C%20and%20there%20were%20political%20spaces%20to%20express%20collective%20feelings.%20Above%20all%2C%20the%20Kashmiri%20identity%2C%20which%20meant%20and%20means%20a%20lot%20to%20a%20Kashmiri%2C%20stayed%20unharmed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2F2023-a-year-of-ironies-and-paradoxes-in-jk%5C%22%3E2023%3A%20A%20Year%20of%20Ironies%20and%20Paradoxes%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECame%20August%202019%2C%20and%20the%20announcement%20was%20made%3B%20the%20special%20status%20given%20to%20Kashmir%20was%20taken%20away.%20A%20high%20and%20mighty%20hand%20of%20Delhi%20was%20all%20that%20it%20needed.%20All%20means%20of%20communication%20were%20severed%3B%20people%20virtually%20locked%20in%20their%20homes.%20Their%20fault%2C%20exactly%20none.%20And%20it%20lasted%20for%20months%2C%20giving%20Kashmiris%20the%20first%20taste%20of%20the%20things%20to%20come.%20The%20legislative%20assembly%20was%20dissolved%20well%20before%20the%20special%20status%20was%20annulled.%20Thousands%20of%20Kashmiris%20were%20jailed%20and%20many%20are%20still%20languishing%20there.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPolitical%20leaders%20were%20arrested%20in%20their%20homes%20and%20all%20political%20activities%20banished.%20The%20resilient%20Kashmiris%20in%20the%20city%2C%20towns%20and%20villages%20survived%20all%20this%2C%20facing%20serious%20difficulties%20including%20access%20to%20high-end%20medical%20care.%20The%20newly%20posted%20bureaucrats%2C%20invariably%20from%20outside%20the%20valley%2C%20were%20made%20to%20administer%20various%20departments.%20Understandably%2C%20they%20had%20very%20little%20idea%20of%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20locals%20especially%20during%20inclement%20weather%20conditions%20and%20difficult%20times.%20Acute%20shortages%20of%20electricity%2C%20snow%20blocking%20roads%20to%20the%20interiors%20and%20sometimes%20even%20shortage%20of%20food%20items%20in%20the%20markets%20%E2%80%93%20these%20were%20just%20some%20of%20the%20things%20Kashmiris%20had%20to%20endure.%20People%20were%20strongly%20discouraged%20from%20expressing%20their%20views%20on%20these%20matters%20and%20prompt%20punitive%20action%20was%20taken%20against%20those%20who%20did.%20The%20local%20press%20was%20severely%20censored%20and%20threatened%20of%20dire%20consequences.%20This%20was%20post-abrogation%20Kashmir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20much%20talked%20about%20development%20and%20progress%20has%20not%20really%20reached%20the%20common%20man.%20Yes%2C%20the%20airport%20road%20has%20improved%2C%20signboards%20are%20better%20and%20tri-colour%20lights%20adorn%20the%20roads.%20But%20the%20houses%20along%20the%20roads%20are%20starved%20of%20electricity.%20The%20%E2%80%98Smart%20City%E2%80%99%20concept%20has%20only%20translated%20to%20changed%20pavement%20tiles%20of%20some%20posh%20shopping%20areas%2C%20illuminating%20one%20side%20of%20the%20famous%20bund%20on%20Jhelum%20and%20replacing%20the%20%3Cem%3Eghantaghar%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20the%20well-known%20Lal%20chowk.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20have%20been%20some%20positive%20developments%20under%20the%20new%20administration%3A%20no%20stone%20pelting%2C%20no%20strikes%2C%20school%20and%20college%20exams%20happening%20on%20time%20etc.%20After%20the%20pandemic%20restrictions%20were%20lifted%2C%C2%A0%20a%20large%20number%20of%20tourists%20came%20to%20the%20valley%20helping%20those%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20connected%20with%20this%20business.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20however%20are%20half-hearted%20measures%20of%20development.%20The%20much%20talked%20about%20investors%20and%20industrialists%20coming%20to%20the%20UT%20with%20mega%20projects%2C%20bringing%20jobs%20and%20prosperity%2C%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20dream.%20Educated%2C%20bright%20youth%20have%20a%20darkness%20to%20face%20with%20very%20few%20suitable%20jobs.%20Their%20parents%20do%20not%20want%20them%20to%20go%20out%20to%20different%20parts%20of%20India%20as%20they%20apprehend%20harm%20in%20a%20hate-filled%20atmosphere%20in%20India%20for%20Muslims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-facade-of-normalcy-exacts-a-heavy-price-from-the-people-of-jammu-and-kashmir%5C%22%3EThe%20Facade%20of%20Normalcy%20Exacts%20a%20Heavy%20Price%20From%20the%20People%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20weekly%20visitor%20to%20my%20home%20in%20Srinagar%2C%20and%20also%20to%20my%20Heart%20Centre%20in%20a%20village%20in%20Pulwama%20district%2C%20I%20have%20been%20a%20witness%20to%20these%20developments%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20However%2C%20this%20winter%20I%20have%20experienced%20the%20misery%20of%20people%20in%20Kashmir%20as%20the%20valley%20reels%20in%20darkness.%20Prolonged%20power%20outages%20and%20freezing%20temperatures%20%E2%80%93%20just%20imagine%20the%20plight.%20Understandably%2C%20many%20people%20want%20to%20move%20to%20Jammu%20for%20a%20few%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20common%20Kashmiri%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20all%20the%20developments%20around%20the%20globe%2C%20is%20still%20dependant%20on%20a%20%3Cem%3Ephiran%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20long%20loose%20robe%20worn%20by%20Kashmiris)%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekangdi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(the%20earthen%20heat%20pot)%20for%20keeping%20themselves%20warm.%20These%20products%20are%20still%20in%20abundant%20use%20even%20after%20500%20years%20of%20their%20introduction%20by%20the%20Mughals%20and%20are%20real%20saviours%20because%20of%20a%20perpetual%20shortage%20of%20electricity%20during%20the%20winter%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20fair%20question%2C%20then%2C%20is%3A%20If%20there%20has%20been%20unprecedented%20development%20in%20the%20region%20and%20people%20are%20immensely%20happy%20with%20the%20abrogation%20%E2%80%93%20as%20is%20being%20propagated%20%E2%80%93%20why%20has%20statehood%20to%20J%26amp%3BK%20not%20been%20restored%3F%20Why%20are%20there%20no%20signs%20of%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20election%20even%20after%20four%20years%20of%20being%20under%20bureaucratic%20rule%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20questions%20beg%20an%20answer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EUpendra%20Kaul%20is%20a%20Kashmiri%20cardiologist.%20He%20is%20a%20recipient%20of%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20and%20the%20Dr%20B.C.%20Roy%20Award.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704245444000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F11100850%2FUntitled-design-14-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Flooking-beyond-politics-constitution-and-law-how-the-people-of-jk-feel-about-scs-decision%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court's%20decision%20to%20uphold%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20has%20been%20welcomed%20by%20those%20in%20the%20mainland.%20What%20about%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3F%20A%20doctor%20shares%20his%20views.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Flooking-beyond-politics-constitution-and-law-how-the-people-of-jk-feel-about-scs-decision%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Japan%20earthquake%3A%20Fires%20hit%20quake%20zone%20as%20rescuers%20race%20to%20reach%20survivors%22%2C%22conte