0were%20how%20quiet%20it%20was%20while%20smoothly%20and%20quickly%20removing%20nose%20and%20ear%20hair.%20It's%20fast%20and%20efficient%20and%20completely%20painless.%20It's%20rechargeable%2C%20easy%20to%20clean%2C%20and%20simple%20to%20operate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20offers%20a%20bundle%20called%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.manscaped.com%2Fproducts%2Fthe-performance-package-4%3F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPerformance%20Package%205.0%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20includes%20the%20Weed%20Whacker%20and%20Lawn%20Mower%2C%20along%20with%20a%20couple%20other%20products%2C%20that%20will%20have%20your%20body%20hair%20removal%20needs%20covered%20from%20nose%20to%20nether%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20lightweight%3Cp%3EThe%20ConairMan%20has%20a%20360-degree%20beveled%20blade%20to%20quickly%20and%20evenly%20cut%20through%20even%20very%20abundant%20nose%20and%20ear%20hair.%20It%20provides%2060-minutes%20of%20continual%20use%2C%20which%20should%20provide%20plenty%20of%20clipping%20sessions.%20Besides%20your%20nose%20and%20ears%2C%20you%20can%20use%20the%20ConairMan%20to%20clean%20up%20the%20rest%20of%20your%20face%2C%20from%20trimming%20and%20shaping%20sideburns%2C%20mustache%20or%20beard%2C%20to%20making%20sure%20your%20brows%20don't%20give%20off%20Neanderthal%20vibes.%20Downsides%20include%20not%20being%20rechargeable%20and%20it%20is%20a%20bit%20loud%2C%20but%20it%20makes%20up%20for%20this%20by%20being%20fast%2C%20lightweight%2C%20and%20multifunctional.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20budget%3Cp%3EThe%20Ginity%20trimmer%20comes%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20benefits%20at%20a%20budget%20price.%20It's%20a%20four-in-one%20grooming%20kit%20so%20you%20can%20trim%20your%20nose%20hairs%20and%20then%20switch%20to%20the%20attachments%20for%20your%20eyebrows%2C%20sideburns%2C%20or%20facial%20hair.%20The%20trimmer%20is%20partially%20waterproof%20(the