own%20as%20president%2C%26quot%3B%20Gay%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20anti-Semitism%20on%20campus%20controversy%20came%20amid%20a%20rise%20in%20attacks%20and%20violent%20rhetoric%20targeting%20Jews%20and%20Muslims%2C%20including%20at%20universities%2C%20since%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20erupted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20of%20Israel%2C%20a%20close%20US%20ally%2C%20has%20claimed%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bwhopping%20wave%20of%20anti-Semitism%26quot%3B%20has%20%26quot%3Bseeped%20onto%20university%20campuses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYad%20Vashem%2C%20Israel's%20official%20Holocaust%20memorial%2C%20has%20described%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcancer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20student%20and%20multi-million-dollar%20donor%20Bill%20Ackman%20claimed%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20Harvard's%20governing%20boards%20that%20%26quot%3BPresident%20Gay's%20failures%20have%20led%20to%20billions%20of%20dollars%20of%20cancelled%2C%20paused%2C%20and%20withdrawn%20donations%20to%20the%20university.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGay%2C%2053%2C%20was%20born%20in%20New%20York%20to%20Haitian%20immigrants%20and%20is%20a%20professor%20of%20political%20science%20who%20in%20July%20became%20the%20first%20Black%20president%20of%20368-year-old%20Harvard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLeadership%20failure%20and%20denial%20of%20anti-Semitism%20have%20a%20price.%20Hope%20glorious%20Harvard%20University%20learns%20from%20this%20dismal%20conduct%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20new%20Israeli%20Foreign%20Minister%20Israel%20Katz%20in%20response%20to%20the%20reports%20of%20Gay's%20imminent%20departure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704222360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-12%2F2c1n352k_harvard-universit