Dubai.%20Cabin%20crew%20were%20praised%20after%20managing%20to%20evacuate%20all%20300%20people%2C%20despite%20the%20panic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Britain's%20Royal%20Aeronautical%20Society%20recommended%20the%20automatic%20locking%20of%20overhead%20bins%20following%20a%20crash%20landing%2C%20noting%20that%20passengers%20often%20ignore%20safety%20briefings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20clearly%20a%20benefit%20if%20you're%20not%20carrying%20your%20baggage%2C%26quot%3B%20Steve%20Creamer%2C%20an%20aviation%20safety%20consultant%20and%20former%20senior%20director%20at%20the%20International%20Civil%20Aviation%20Organization%20(ICAO)%2C%20said%20following%20Tuesday's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjapan-airlines-flight-seen-in-flames-on-tokyo-airports-runway-4786079%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_bigstory%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETokyo%20crash%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20pretty%20remarkable%20that%20they%20got%20everybody%20off%20the%20airplane.%20That%20says%20a%20lot%20about%20the%20flight%20crew%20and%20the%20discipline%20of%20the%20people%20on%20board.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704218700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F67a14qkg_tokyo-plane-collision_625x300_02_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmiracle-evacuation-from-burning-japan-jet-helped-by-fliers-leaving-bags-4788871%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Video%20showed%20passengers%20being%20evacuated%20from%20the%20burning%20Airbus%20A350%20by%20escape%20slides%20in%20relative%20calm%20and%20apparently%20without%20hand%20luggage%2C%20in%20an%20operation%20hailed%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmiracle%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%