s%20sent%20false%20alarms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fwhy-almost-150-earthquakes-struck-japan-in-less-than-a-day%2Farticleshow%2F106491970.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fwhy-almost-150-earthquakes-struck-japan-in-less-than-a-day%2Famp_articleshow%2F106491970.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fwhy-almost-150-earthquakes-struck-japan-in-less-than-a-day%2Famp_articleshow%2F106491970.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20Directs%20Bihar%20Government%20to%20Make%20Public%20Break-Up%20of%20Caste%20Survey%20Data%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20directed%20the%20Bihar%20government%20to%20make%20the%20break-up%20of%20its%20caste%20survey%20data%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20to%20enable%20those%20aggrieved%20to%20challenge%20the%20findings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20division%20Bench%20of%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Justice%20Dipankar%20Datta%2C%20however%2C%20declined%20the%20petitioners%E2%80%99s%20plea%20for%20interim%20relief%3B%20the%20petitioners%20had%20challenged%20the%20survey%20and%20Patna%20high%20court%20order%20that%20upheld%20the%20Bihar%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20conduct%20such%20an%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20question%20of%20interim%20relief%20as%20they%20(the%20government)%20have%20a%20high%20court%20order%20in%20their%20favour.%20Now%20that%20the%20data%20has%20been%20put%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20there%20are%20two%20to%20three%20aspects%20which%20remain.%20First%20is%20the%20legal%20issue%20%E2%80%93%20the%20correctness%20of%20the%20high%20court%20judgement%20and%20legality%20of%20such%20an%20exercise%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Bench%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fbihar-caste-survey-break-up-public-domain-inferences-challenged-sc-9092151%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20PTI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Raju%20Ramachandran%2C%20who%20appeared%20for%20the%20petitioners%2C%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20court%20that%20the%20authorities%20had%20already%20begun%20implementing%20survey%20findings%20since%20the%20data%20was%20already%20out.%20He%20said%20the%20state%20government%20had%20already%20raised%20the%20reservation%20for%20SCs%2C%20STs%2C%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%2C%20Extremely%20Backward%20Classes%2C%20and%20Economically%20Weaker%20Sections%20(EWS)%20to%20a%20total%20of%2075%25%20from%20the%20existing%2050%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%2C%20the%20court%20said%20the%20matter%20about%20the%20increase%20in%20the%20reservation%20should%20be%20challenged%20before%20the%20Patna%20high%20court%2C%20and%20said%20the%20entire%20matter%20needs%20to%20be%20heard%20at%20length.%20The%20counsel%20for%20the%20petitioners%20in%20response%20said%20that%20they%20had%20already%20moved%20the%20high%20court%2C%20challenging%20the%20increase%20in%20the%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20it%20as%20an%20important%20issue%2C%20Ramachandran%20said%20since%20the%20state%20government%20is%20already%20acting%20upon%20the%20data%2C%20the%20matter%20be%20listed%20next%20week%20so%20that%20the%20petitioners%20can%20argue%20for%20interim%20relief.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20interim%20relief%3F%20They%20(the%20Bihar%20government)%20have%20a%20high%20court%20judgement%20in%20their%20favour%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Bench%20said%20in%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Bihar%20government%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%2C%20Shyam%20Divan%2C%20submitted%20to%20the%20court%20that%20the%20data%2C%20including%20the%20break-up%2C%20has%20been%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20and%20anyone%20can%20see%20it%20on%20the%20designated%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20for%20the%20Bench%2C%20Justice%20Khanna%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20am%20more%20worried%20about%20is%20the%20availability%20of%20break-up%20of%20data.%20To%20what%20extent%20the%20government%20can%20withhold%20the%20data%3F%20You%20see%2C%20the%20entire%20break-up%20of%20data%20should%20be%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20so%20that%20anyone%20can%20challenge%20the%20inference%20drawn%20from%20it.%20Unless%20it%20is%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20challenge%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20been%20accusing%20the%20Nitish%20Kumar%20government%20of%20irregularities%20in%20conducting%20the%20caste%20survey%20and%20calling%20the%20data%20collected%20%E2%80%9Cfake%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bench%20then%20told%20Divan%20to%20file%20a%20report%20on%20the%20caste%20survey%20and%20posted%20the%20matter%20for%20further%20hearing%20on%20February%205.%20The%20caste%20survey%20revealed%20that%20the%20OBCs%20and%20EBCs%20constituted%20a%20whopping%2063%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704205839000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsc-directs-bihar-government-to-make-public-break-up-of-caste-survey-data%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20division%20Bench%20of%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Justice%20Dipankar%20Datta%20said%20unless%20such%20data%20is%20available%20in%20public%20domain%20those%20aggrieved%20by%20it%20cannot%20challenge%20its%20findings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsc-directs-bihar-government-to-make-public-break-up-of-caste-survey-data