20chief%20minister%20has%20been%20rendered%20symbolic%20by%20the%20deforestation%20drive%20in%20Hasdeo%20Arand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShukla%20said%20that%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20mining%20for%20PEKB%20affects%20the%20Ghatbarra%20village%2C%20which%20will%20be%20%E2%80%9Cdisplaced%20entirely%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20today%2C%20the%20Ghatbarra%20gram%20sabha%20has%20not%20given%20its%20consent%20for%20mining%20in%20the%20area.%20%5BIt%20is%5D%20right%20next%20to%20that%20Parsa%20coal%20block%3B%20%5Bit%5D%20will%20affect%20three%20villages%2C%20which%20have%20been%20agitating%20%5Bagainst%20mining%5D%20for%20five%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShukla%E2%80%99s%20organisation%20had%20previously%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fhasdeo-aranya-mining-clearance-centre-trampling-on-tribal-rights-say-activists%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Forest%20Rights%20Act%20of%202006%2C%20completion%20of%20the%20forest%20rights%20claims%20process%20and%20obtaining%20written%20consent%20from%20the%20concerned%20gram%20sabhas%20(village%20councils)%20are%20mandatory%20before%20granting%20forest%20clearance%20for%20any%20project.%20They%20alleged%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fhasdeo-protests-against-tree-felling-continue-fir-against-activists-for-rioting%5C%22%3Efake%20consent%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20obtained%20from%20the%20gram%20sabhas%20in%20the%20Hasdeo%20Arand%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202021%2C%20hundreds%20of%20villagers%20from%20the%20Hasdeo%20Arand%20area%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fhasdeo-aranya-mining-clearance-centre-trampling-on-tribal-rights-say-activists%5C%22%3Ehad%20walked%20300%20kms%20to%20Raipur%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20protest%20against%20mining%20in%20the%20area.%20They%20had%20met%20then%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20and%20governor%20Anasuya%20Uikey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20October%2023%2C%202021%2C%20the%20governor%20wrote%20to%20the%20chief%20secretary%20to%20probe%20these%20fake%20consents%2C%20however%2C%20no%20enquiry%20has%20been%20done.%20So%2C%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20nothing%20has%20been%20done%20to%20give%20justice%20to%20the%20Adivasis%20in%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shukla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20July%2026%2C%202022%2C%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20assembly%20passed%20a%20unanimous%20resolution%20that%20mining%20activities%20will%20not%20be%20carried%20out%20in%20Hasdeo.%20But%20unfortunately%2C%20deforestation%20activities%20have%20now%20started%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShukla%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-new-mining-reserves-required-in-hasdeo-chhattisgarh-tells-sc-101689706977387.html%5C%22%3Eaffidavit%20%3C%2Fa%3E%20submitted%20by%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20government%20in%20July%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20wherein%20it%20was%20stated%20that%2C%20aside%20from%20the%20PEKB%20project%2C%20there%20is%20no%20necessity%20to%20allocate%20or%20use%20any%20new%20mining%20reserve%20areas%20for%20mining%20in%20Hasdeo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhether%20it%20is%20a%20resolution%20passed%20unanimously%20by%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20assembly%2C%20or%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20affidavit%2C%20or%20overlooking%20the%20gram%20sabhas%E2%80%99%20opposition%2C%20all%20efforts%20have%20become%20null%20and%20void%20in%20the%20face%20of%20corporate%20interests%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Raipur-based%20political%20commentator%2C%20who%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20be%20named%2C%20said%20that%20in%20terms%20of%20taking%20away%20the%20Adivasi%20community%E2%80%99s%20rights%20over%20land%20for%20corporate%20interests%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20are%20taking%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20work%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20government%20had%20taken%20the%20BJP%20government%E2%80%99s%20(Raman%20Singh%20government%2C%20from%202013%20to%202018)%20work%20forward%20and%20now%20the%20BJP%20is%20taking%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20work%20forward.%20In%20the%20area%20where%20deforestation%20is%20taking%20place%20now%2C%20under%20the%20Congress%20regime%2C%2043%20hectares%20of%20trees%20were%20cut%20last%20year%20(2022).%20In%20the%20same%20area%2C%2091%20acres%20were%20cut%20this%20year%20(2023).%20Now%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20is%20here.%20There%20is%20nothing%20new%20with%20the%20new%20government%20or%20with%20a%20new%20tribal%20chief%20minister%20or%20a%20previous%20non-tribal%20chief%20minister%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20several%20villages%20that%20are%20not%20part%20of%20Hasdeo%20but%20are%20part%20of%20Raipur%2C%20Bilaspur%2C%20Kanker%2C%20Durg%20zilas%2C%20villagers%20are%20ready%20to%20take%20out%20protest%20marches%20apart%20from%20the%20organisations%20working%20to%20protect%20Hasdeo.%20These%20protests%20will%20likely%20intensify%20as%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20continue%20to%20shift%20the%20blame%20to%20each%20other%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fin-chhattishgarh-adanis-coal-mine-leaves-a-village-parched-this-monsoon%5C%22%3EIn%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20Coal%20Mine%20Leaves%20a%20Village%20Parched%20This%20Monsoon%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdivasi%20anger%20fuelled%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20victory%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20November%20state%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-chhattisgarh-congresss-cautious-pessimism-proves-to-be-too-little-too-late%5C%22%3Eunseated%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Congress%20government%20by%20winning%2054%20of%20the%2090%20assembly%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20only%20managed%20to%20win%20only%2035%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20approximately%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftribal.nic.in%2FST%2FTribal%2520Profile.pdf%5C%22%3E30%25%20of%20the%20population%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20tribals%2C%20the%20state%20witnessed%20the%20appointment%20of%20its%20first%20tribal%20chief%20minister%2C%20Sai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20which%20won%2025%20of%20the%2029%20reserved%20seats%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%20in%20the%202018%20assembly%20polls%2C%20secured%20only%2011%20this%20time.%20The%20BJP%20improved%20its%20tally%20from%20three%20in%202018%20to%2017%20seats%20dominated%20by%20tribals%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVeteran%20tribal%20leader%20and%20former%20Union%20minister%20Arvind%20Netam%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fchhattisgarh-adivasis-bjp-congress-arvind-netam%5C%22%3Ewho%20quit%20the%20Congress%20last%20year%20to%20float%20his%20own%20political%20outfit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Hamar%20Raj%20Party%2C%20said%20that%20the%20reason%20behind%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20loss%20in%20these%20elections%20was%20its%20neglect%20of%20the%20tribal%20community%20and%20dilution%20of%20the%20Panchayat%20Extension%20to%20Scheduled%20Areas%20(PESA)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PESA%20law%2C%20passed%20in%201996%2C%20seeks%20to%20provide%20a%20sense%20of%20autonomy%20to%20the%20local%20Adivasis%20by%20making%20the%20consent%20of%20the%20gram%20sabhas%20in%20Adivasi%20areas%20mandatory%20for%20projects%20in%20the%20region.%20When%20the%20Congress%20government%20notified%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fchhattisgarh-govt-implements-pesa-rule-2022%2Farticle65751589.ece%5C%22%3Eimplemented%20the%20PESA%20rules%20in%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%20(almost%2025%20years%20after%20the%20law%20was%20passed)%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cconsent%E2%80%9D%20of%20gram%20sabhas%20was%20changed%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fcongress-chhattisgarh-pesa-rules-activist-fire-8087658%2F%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%9Cconsultation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20behind%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20victory%20in%20the%20tribal%20areas%20is%20that%20the%20previous%20Congress%20government%20neglected%20the%20tribal%20community.%20Under%20the%20PESA%20law%2C%20the%20tribal%20community%20was%20granted%20rights%20and%20control%20over%20jal%20(water)%2C%20jungle%20(forest)%2C%20and%20zameen%20(land)%2C%20but%20the%20Congress%20government%20diluted%20these%20provisions.%20This%20was%20the%20primary%20issue%20that%20led%20to%20the%20downfall%20of%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20the%20state.%20In%20Bastar%2C%20at%20least%2020-22%20places%20have%20ongoing%20andolan%20(agitation)%20for%20over%20a%20year%20on%20jal%2C%20jungle%2C%20zameen.%20Either%20completely%20abolish%20PESA%2C%20or%20as%20long%20as%20the%20law%20exists%2C%20people%20will%20continue%20to%20speak%20up%2C%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20Netam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F23175928%2FWhatsApp-Image-2021-10-23-at-5.54.23-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F23175928%2FWhatsApp-Image-2021-10-23-at-5.54.23-PM.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F23175928%2FWhatsApp-Image-2021-10-23-at-5.54.23-PM-300x135.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F23175928%2FWhatsApp-Image-2021-10-23-at-5.54.23-PM-1024x461.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-560107%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22540%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20padyatra%20against%20mining%20in%20Hasdeo%20Aranya%2C%20held%20in%20October%202021.%20Photo%3A%20Chhattisgarh%20Bachao%20Andolan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShukla%20said%20that%20along%20with%20the%20dilution%20of%20the%20PESA%20law%2C%20which%20angered%20Adivasis%20who%20had%20voted%20for%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%9Cwith%20a%20lot%20of%20hope%E2%80%9D%20in%202018%2C%20it%20also%20failed%20to%20act%20decisively%20against%20Hindutva%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBastar%E2%80%99s%20Narayanpur%20emerged%20as%20the%20epicentre%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20claims%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fraipur%2Fmass-conversions-in-chhattisgarh-under-congress-govt-amit-shah%2Farticleshow%2F103315610.cms%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cforced%20conversions%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Christian%20missionaries%20in%20the%20tribal%20regions%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fprotests-in-chhattisgarhs-narayanpur-over-coordinated-anti-christian-violence%5C%22%3E%2020%20instances%20of%20anti-Christian%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20reported%20from%20the%20Narayanpur%20district%20in%20December%202022%20alone.%20A%20church%20in%20Narayanpur%20was%20vandalised%20in%20January%202023.%20Ahead%20of%20the%20elections%2C%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchhattisgarh-adivasi-christians-struggle-conversion-bogey-narayanpur%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20in%20Narayanpur%E2%80%99s%20villages%2C%20Adivasis%2C%20who%20had%20converted%20to%20Christianity%2C%20continued%20to%20struggle%20to%20bury%20their%20dead%20and%20faced%20social%20boycott.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Narayanpur%2C%20the%20Congress%20was%20following%20soft%20Hindutva%20and%20did%20not%20act%20to%20protect%20those%20who%20had%20converted%20to%20Christianity.%20Riots%20were%20reported%2C%20apart%20from%20attacks%20on%20church%2C%20and%20not%20allowing%20burials%20of%20those%20who%20had%20converted%20to%20Christianity.%20While%20the%20Hindutva%20supporters%20in%20the%20region%20were%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP%20anyway%2C%20the%20Adivasi%20Christians%20were%20also%20disappointed%20because%20no%20action%20was%20taken%20to%20protect%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shukla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Bastar-based%20lawyer%20and%20activist%20Bela%20Bhatia%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20policies%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20haven%E2%80%99t%20acted%20differently%20for%20the%20tribal%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Adivasi%20community%20expected%20an%20adequate%20shift%20when%20the%20Congress%20came%20to%20power.%20It%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fchhattisgarh-christians-hindutva-communalism%5C%22%3Enot%20that%20attacks%20on%20Christians%20were%20new%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20they%20increased%20during%20the%20Congress%20years%2C%20and%20the%20government%20did%20not%20handle%20it%20boldly%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActivists%20said%20that%20Adivasi%20anger%20against%20the%20Congress%20government%20also%20intensified%20due%20to%20its%20inaction%20on%20judicial%20inquiry%20reports%20regarding%20fake%20encounters%20that%20occurred%20under%20the%20previous%20BJP%20government.%20These%20reports%20surfaced%20during%20the%20Baghel%20years%20but%20were%20not%20addressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202012%2C%2017%20villagers%20were%20gunned%20down%20in%20an%20alleged%20encounter%20between%20security%20forces%20and%20alleged%20Maoists%20in%20Barstar%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbastar-fake-encounter-maoists-inquiry%5C%22%3ESarkeguda.%3C%2Fa%3E%20A%20judicial%20inquiry%20report%20by%20retired%20Justice%20V.K.%20Agarwal%20in%202019%20found%20that%20there%20was%20no%20evidence%20to%20suggest%20that%20those%20who%20were%20killed%20or%20injured%20by%20security%20forces%20were%20Maoists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20inquiry%20report%20by%20Justice%20Agarwal%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjudicial-enquiry-finds-victims-of-chhattisgarh-were-not-maoists%5C%22%3EEdesmetta%20encounter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20which%20eight%20tribals%20were%20killed%20on%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%20May%2017%20and%2018%2C%202013%2C%20when%20the%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20opened%20fire%20on%20villagers%20who%20had%20gathered%20to%20celebrate%20%3Cem%3Ebeej%20pandum%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Edesmetta%2C%20also%20concluded%20that%20none%20of%20the%20eight%20people%20killed%20were%20Maoists%20and%20that%20the%20security%20forces%20may%20have%20opened%20fire%20on%20the%20unarmed%20crowd%20in%20a%20moment%20of%20panic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20judicial%20inquiry%20reports%20being%20submitted%20during%20the%20Congress%20rule%2C%20no%20action%20was%20taken%20to%20provide%20justice%20to%20the%20Adivasis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhatia%20referred%20to%20recent%20incidents%20in%20which%20villagers%20have%20been%20caught%20in%20the%20fray%20of%20counter-insurgency%20measures%20against%20left-wing%20extremism%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20three%20crucial%20ways%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20governments%20have%20been%20similar%3A%20in%20terms%20of%20economic%20policies%2C%20counter-insurgency%20measures%2C%20and%20lack%20of%20respect%20for%20people%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20justice%20and%20grievance%20redressal%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20villagers%20in%20Sukma%E2%80%99s%20Tadmetla%20protested%20against%20the%20killing%20of%20two%20men%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fchhattisgarh-villagers-protest-death-of-2-in-tadmetla-say-they-weren-t-maoists-101694446947398.html%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cfake%20encounter%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fa%3Eafter%20police%20claimed%20that%20they%20were%20Maoists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20October%2C%20two%20youngsters%20from%20Abujhmad%20village%20were%20also%20killed%20allegedly%20in%20an%20encounter.%20In%20fact%2C%20they%20had%20accompanied%20their%20mothers%20to%20the%20ration%20shop%2C%20a%20day%E2%80%99s%20walk%20away%20in%20Koelibeda%2C%20so%20that%20they%20could%20carry%20the%20load%20of%20grain%20home.%20They%20were%20taken%20away%20in%20front%20of%20their%20mothers.%20The%20mothers%20heard%20the%20shots%20and%20also%20saw%20the%20dead%20bodies%20when%20they%20were%20carried%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlmost%20every%20other%20day%20we%20keep%20hearing%20of%20activists%20and%20participants%20of%20peaceful%20protests%20being%20picked%20up%20and%20some%20of%20them%20incarcerated%20under%20false%20charges.%20This%20was%20the%20case%20before%20and%20after%20the%20change%20of%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Adivasis%20need%20control%20over%20their%20%3Cem%3Ejal%2C%20jungle%2C%20zameen%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20for%20this%2C%20PESA%20and%20the%20Forest%20Rights%20Act%20need%20to%20be%20implemented%20in%20letter%20and%20spirit.%20The%20way%20the%20government%20is%20going%20ahead%20with%20privatisation%20without%20adhering%20to%20these%20laws%20and%20opening%20security%20camps%20in%20many%20places%2C%20it%20is%20apparent%20that%20they%20are%20protecting%20mining%20companies%20and%20not%20the%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetam%20said%20that%20the%20true%20test%20for%20the%20new%20chief%20minister%20being%20from%20the%20tribal%20community%20himself%20will%20be%20how%20he%20handles%20these%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20understand%20is%20that%20there%20is%20not%20much%20difference%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20on%20%3Cem%3Ejal%2C%20jungle%2C%20zameen.%20%3C%2Fem%3EBut%20how%20much%20will%20he%20(Sai)%20be%20able%20to%20resist%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20policies%20and%20make%20pro-tribal%20policies%2C%20only%20time%20will%20tell.%20This%20will%20be%20the%20test%20for%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20because%20they%20%5Bthe%20BJP%5D%20have%20governments%20both%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20in%20the%20state%20now.%20Earlier%2C%20they%20could%20deflect%20blame%20to%20each%20other%2C%20despite%20both%20being%20pro-capitalist%20in%20their%20policies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20Adivasis%20reach%20positions%20of%20power%2C%20it%20is%20welcome%2C%20but%20the%20real%20test%20is%20whether%20their%20coming%20to%20power%20makes%20a%20difference%20to%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20Adivasis%2C%20and%20if%20they%20will%20prove%20themselves%20to%20be%20better%20than%20their%20predecessors%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhatia%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704200457000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F10192940%2FGA6N65IaQAAU8Yf.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhasdeo-arand-deforestation-raises-questions-of-adivasi-justice-for-chhattisgarhs-first-tribal-cm%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20section%20of%20activists%20fighting%20for%20Adivasi%20rights%20in%20the%20state%20believe%20that%20there%20is%20no%20point%20in%20having%20a%20tribal%20chief%20minister%20if%20he%20continues%20to%20overlook%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20priorities%20to%20facilitate%20corporate%20interests%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhasdeo-arand-deforestation-raises-questions-of-adivasi-justice-for-chhattisgarhs-first-tribal-cm%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'It%20was%20hell'%3A%20Passengers%20describe%20horror%20on%20board%20burning%20plane%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704199680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F70x70%2Fskynews-interior-japan-plane-fire_6410240.jpg%3F20240102144958%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fjapan-plane-fire-passengers-describe-horror-on-board-burning-aircraft-13040923%22%2C%22summary%22