9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLike%20Moko%E2%80%99s%20grandmother%20who%20spoke%20of%20her%20experience%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Khezhakeno%20village%20in%20Phek%20district%2C%20my%20late%20maternal%20grandmother%20also%20used%20to%20narrate%20stories%20of%20when%20the%20Japanese%20troops%20entered%20her%20village%20of%20Jakhama.%20It%20was%20a%20traumatic%20time%20in%20their%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Asalie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_357823542_1259424638023921_5888304989041501718_n_1080-1700749912.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Moko%20Koza%20with%20his%20grandmother.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_357823542_1259424638023921_5888304989041501718_n_1080-1700749912.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_357823542_1259424638023921_5888304989041501718_n_1080-1700749912-300x253.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_357823542_1259424638023921_5888304989041501718_n_1080-1700749912-500x421.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_357823542_1259424638023921_5888304989041501718_n_1080-1700749912-768x646.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_357823542_1259424638023921_5888304989041501718_n_1080-1700749912-150x126.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334846%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22909%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMoko%20Koza%20with%20his%20grandmother.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20Moko%20does%20a%20great%20job%20of%20being%20musically%20relevant